  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>General</Type>
    <Text>Hotel Facility and Services inclusive of Business Center with fully equipment and function, Gym, Sauna, Car Rental, Laundry Service, Beauty Parlor and Travel Agent Counter facility also available here.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>SurroundingArea</Type>
    <Text>The perfect environment for both business and leisure easily accessible by Skytrain and river transportation and provides convenient access to the major thoroughfares  of Silom , Sathorn and Rama III roads, the expressway links to Suvarnabhumi  International Airport (only 45 minutes away).</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>RoomTypes</Type>
    <Text>All rooms offer excellent luxuries and comforts with the finest international standard facilities which will make the guest have a memorable time during their stay. In room amenities inclusive of Individual telephone with voicemail, two IDD telephone-lines, high speed wi-fi internet connection access in all suite, flat-screen LCD televation with HDMI (high definition multi-screen interface) etc. Grand Room City View is spacious with 60 sqm including private balcony. Floor-to-ceiling windows that afford both optimal daylight and breathtaking view of the cityscape. Rooms feature fully kitchenette and five-star amenities. Bathrooms are luxurious with separate tub and shower.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>PropertyInformation</Type>
    <Text>The 36 storey in building modern style located along the Chao Phraya River.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>DiningFacilities</Type>
    <Text>The hotel features a variety of restaurants for you to choose service "River Barge Restaurant offer international cuisines and regional specialties opening: 06.00 a.m.-01.00 a.m., and The Chinese Restaurant or Silver Waves Restaurant specializes in authentic Cantonese cuisines " etc.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>Short</Type>
    <Text>Hotel offers medium size lobby with a really cozy ambience and a large lotus pond and lush tropical garden to relax, mix and mingle.</Text>
